<article id="article" class="article "><header><h1 class="title" itemprop="headline">Michael Bloomberg's net worth is $47B, how will he use it?</h1>

					<p class="dek">The media mogul says most of his fortune will go to his foundation &ndash; viewing personal philanthropy not as a threat to democracy, but a way to get things done</p>
		
    </header><div class="social sharebar_expanded inline-sharebar theme-light  location-top" data-component="sharebar">

